Game demo proposal for Allegro.pas 5 by Handoko.
There are several changes by Guillermo Martinez, mainly code reordering.

This game is open source. But if you want to distribute the contents, you should check their license terms:

http://www.reinerstilesets.de/2d-grafiken/2d-humans/
https://opengameart.org/content/village-in-the-valley
https://opengameart.org/content/fantasy-book
http://tulrich.com/fonts/
https://opengameart.org/content/dark-untilted-remix
https://opengameart.org/content/3-melee-sounds
https://opengameart.org/content/5-hit-sounds-dying

History:
- 31 July 2017, RC3 - Fix background audio issue
- 18 July 2017, RC2 - Double sized window on large screen
- 18 July 2017, RC2 - Use ctrl keys instead of shift keys
- 10 July 2017, RC1 - Use 60 fixed fps
